reviews.review_text:
California Earthquake! Thanx Alabama Bob & Andrew.  I listened to this one the same day as LA shook with a 5.4.
This is a huge upgrade from my cassettes but still not a stellar sounding copy.  I remember the show being good but I left thinking it was not too much out of the ordinary.  Clarence usually seemed to drag the band down a bit.  
Highlights are Shakedown, Victim, Terrapin, and the outro jam from Standing on the Moon.  Peace
